name: Mike Slott - Lucky 9 Teen (Limited Japanese Edition with Bonus tracks)
description:
Limited Japanese Edition CD of Mike Slott's Lucky 9 Teen record


Mike Slott has expanded his Lucky 9Teen release into a true full-length. The first LuckyMe CD release is available across Japan now with a super limited amount available here.

Care of the excellent photographic company, Powershovel, it comes with a booklet of photographs shot by Mike himself around New York. 

The two new tracks, Dee & Cat Nap point towards another good year for Mike in 2011
